Speaker: Ingo Stegmaier Track:PyConDE This 30-minute talk will give you an overview about project management, success factors and specialties within enterprises. This will be a guide how you promote internal projects and bring them to success within a highly "political" environment. Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2019 conference. https://pycon.de More details at the conference page: https://de.pycon.org/program/XJLSWG Twitter: https://twitter.com/pydataberlin Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconde
